OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 32 years after
OL,4,Cmetal pole attack on sleeping students
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed for a
OL,7,Fcombined total of 32 years following a
OL,8,F"brutal and shocking" attack on
OL,9,Fstudents inside their own home in
OL,10,FSouthampton.
OL,12,FBrian Mitchell, 50, and Kyle Rice, 26,
OL,13,Fbroke into the student accommodation
OL,14,Fin the Portswood area during the early
OL,15,Fhours of 3 January 2026, while the
OL,16,Fvictims were fast asleep.
OL,18,FAfter stealing laptops, mobile phones,
OL,19,Fand bank cards, the intruders forced
OL,20,Fthe students into another room.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
