OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 32 years after
OL,4,Cmetal pole attack on sleeping students
OL,6,FThe victims were then repeatedly
OL,7,Fstruck with a metal pole in a violent
OL,8,Fattack.
OL,10,FThe break-in was part of a wider crime
OL,11,Fspree that night. After targeting the
OL,12,Fstudent property, Mitchell and Rice
OL,13,Fbroke into a nearby business, stealing
OL,14,Fcash and a bicycle.
OL,16,FHowever, a local resident reported
OL,17,Fseeing two men acting suspiciously in
OL,18,Fthe area over several hours and was
OL,19,Flater able to identify both defendants.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
