OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784211519
OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 32 years after
OL,4,Cmetal pole attack on sleeping students
OL,6,FPolice officers arrested Mitchell and
OL,7,FRice just three hours after the attack.
OL,9,FWhen they searched the address where
OL,10,Fthey were located, they recovered the
OL,11,Fstolen items along with blood-stained
OL,12,Fclothing.
OL,14,FThe pair pleaded guilty after facing a
OL,15,Fmountain of evidence against them,
OL,16,Fincluding CCTV footage, witness
OL,17,Ftestimony, forensic evidence, and
OL,18,Fpositive identifications.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
