OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 32 years after
OL,4,Cmetal pole attack on sleeping students
OL,6,FAt Southampton Crown Court today,
OL,7,FBrian Mitchell was jailed for 17
OL,8,Fyears, and Kyle Rice was jailed for 15
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Karen
OL,12,FFairley from the Crown Prosecution
OL,13,FService said: "This was a shocking and
OL,14,Fviolent attack carried out while the
OL,15,Fvictims slept in their own home.
OL,17,F"Brian Mitchell and Kyle Rice showed a
OL,18,Fcomplete disregard for human life.
OL,19,FThey broke into a home, used a weapon
OL,20,Fand inflicted devastating harm simply
OL,21,Fto steal property.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
