CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784211519
OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 32 years after
OL,4,Cmetal pole attack on sleeping students
OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service built a
OL,7,Fcase of CCTV footage, powerful witness
OL,8,Fevidence and identification evidence,
OL,9,Fwhich left the defendants with no
OL,10,Foption but to admit their guilt."
OL,12,FThe stolen bicycle taken from the
OL,13,Flocal business has since been
OL,14,Frecovered by police and returned to
OL,15,Fits owner.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
